## Full Docs per Module
### Crc32

checksum : List U8 -> U32

Description:
Calculate CRC32 checksum for a byte array.

    Crc32.checksum(Str.to_utf8("123456789"))  # 0xCBF43926
    Crc32.checksum([0x00])                    # 0xD202EF8D
    Crc32.checksum([])                        # 0
